    public abstract static class Caltech101.Record<IMAGE extends Image<?,IMAGE>>
extends Object
implements Identifiable, ImageProvider<IMAGE>
    A record in the Caltech 101 dataset. Contains the image together with (optional) metadata on the bounds of the object in the image as well as the class of object in the image.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
